data.description:
Welcome to your future home in the heart of Bristolville, Ohio! This cozy 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom property is now available for sale, offering an excellent opportunity for homeowners and investors alike.

This property is being sold in "As Is" condition, providing you with the chance to customize and update it according to your preferences and needs. Whether you're looking to invest, renovate, or make it your forever home, this property has incredible potential.
Property includes 2 lots:
1. 6431 Morrell Ray Rd Bristolville, OH 44402 (Main listing) 
a. Parcel number: 35065100
b. Lot size: 51,836sqft
2. MORRELL RAY CORTLAND, OH 44410 (land to be included in sale)
a. Parcel number: 35065050
b. Lot size: 129,809sqft
